Pong (Ataria - 1972)
=========

Unity
Commands:
    f - focus in object


=========

Consist in six items:

2 - scores ( player 1 and player 2)
2 - paddles
1 - ball
1 - net

Imagem: https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&source=imgres&cd=&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=2ahUKEwja7JTniNPgAhXiHLkGHehfA9EQjRx6BAgBEAU&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Finside-story-of-pong-excerpt%2F&psig=AOvVaw2yo41z1EZyMQN0aFeQhcvG&ust=1551052993424603


Players:
    - Control the paddles;
    - Move paddles to up and down to tryind to make contact with the ball;

Score:
    - Show the points make by the players;

Ball:
    - Move over table;

Net:
    - Divide the table;

Phisics:
    - There is no gravity, friction and no spin effect;


* Classic Game Design Rule 1: 
    - The Simple Rule: Keep it simple.

* Classic Game Design Rule 2: 
    - Immediate Gameplay Rule: Start gameplay immediately.

